  "title": "Administrative Officer",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a responsible and detail-oriented Admin Officer to support Company daily administrative operations. Reporting to the HR & Admin Manager, this role involves admin support, data entry, and general office administration.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Perform accurate data entry and maintain proper documentation</li><li>Assist in general administrative and HR support duties</li><li>Handle office administration,filing, and record keeping</li><li>Prepare simple reports and spreadsheets</li><li>Support daily office operation and ad-hoc tasks</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Minimum GCE ‘O’ Level / Diploma or equivalent</li><li>Good computer skills are a must, especially Microsoft Word & Excel</li><li>Good typing, organisational, and time management skills</li><li>Detail-oriented, responsible, and able to handle confidential information</li><li>Fresh graduates are welcome to apply</li></ul><p>.</p>",
