    "description": "<p>CKS PROPERTY CONSULTANTS PTE LTD</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We a full-fledged property consultancy firm. We provide professional services across the residential, commercial, industrial and retail property sectors. With our expanding office network, we are well positioned to facilitate cross-border transactions and investments in regional markets.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>CKS is also part of the global PhillipCapital network, a global integrated financial services group catering to retail, corporate and institutional clients. Our intimate business relationship with PhillipCapital affords us the opportunity to leverage on their considerable financial resources and customer network.</p>",
